      "Text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "\nThe SUSE Linux Enterprise 15 SP7 kernel was updated to fix the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2026-43284: xfrm: esp: avoid in-place decrypt on shared skb frags (bsc#1264449).\n",
